{"tid":1686571,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"楊潤雄就教育局發禁蒙面法通告至幼稚園致歉","createTime":"2019-11-01T08:23:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T08:35:50.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"aec1a388bf23775b288cef5d635821e814530e39","tid":1686571,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T08:23:50.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】教育局上月初要求全港中學，提交戴口罩、罷課或參與校外人鏈的人數，局長楊潤雄在立法會教育事務委員會上表示，局方鑑於近期情況改善，並沒有再主動詢問每間學校的狀況。<br />\n<br />\n被問到局方早前將有關禁蒙面法的通告發送至幼稚園，楊潤雄指由於時間倉促，承認幼稚園學生並沒有戴口罩到街上所衍生的風險，有就事件向幼稚園校長道歉。<br />\n<br />\n多名建制派議員亦關注有學生參與近期暴力衝突。<br />\n<br />\n被問到是否需要成立危機小組處理，楊潤雄指現時局方每天有就事件進行討論。<br />\n<br />\n對於港大畢業生議會通過要求行政長官林鄭月娥辭任校監，楊潤雄指十年前曾作檢討，暫時看不到要再討論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=368360\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D368360&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvG9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=9449371d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D368360&h=07d596a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=368360</a>"},{"pid":"61deeb8c0bbbc8d38f3a387bae4e5bd9b8965abb","tid":1686571,"uid":4942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T08:24:48.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<br />\n<br />\n垃圾"},{"pid":"f2302c6671cc6a30d5a2078be4fc2e61cb257b22","tid":1686571,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T08:32:01.000Z","msg":"曱甴王近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93530f80a912f1ea8da7c0678a5693d7cf57a581","tid":1686571,"uid":22535,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T08:32:33.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"68f704a709250db598f3f0a3593e2f02eb5ed371","tid":1686571,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T08:33:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a3cb567dc7e9b6aba84351575db4dbe35d5978d","tid":1686571,"uid":105511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T08:33:36.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"db48e0fc799cd544e91f4e39e74ddccbb88d813f","tid":1686571,"uid":264915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T08:34:02.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"1d48ca03c84cd5bc333b6b729557c247e08ec8e3","tid":1686571,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T08:34:33.000Z","msg":"有就事件向幼稚園校長道歉<br />\n<br />\n校長咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a566260ce00225fcc083d5d9b8f9dd5c4fae01cd","tid":1686571,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T08:35:50.000Z","msg":"如果唔係流感同手足口病<br />\n佢唔會道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}